Package org.neo4j.internal.recordstorage

Class RecordStorageReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.internal.recordstorage.RecordStorageReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable, StorageReader, StorageSchemaReader
    public class RecordStorageReader
extends Object
implements StorageReader
    Default implementation of StorageReader. Delegates to NeoStores and indexes.

      • schemaSnapshot

        public StorageSchemaReader schemaSnapshot()
        Description copied from interface: StorageReader
        Get a lock-free snapshot of the current schema, for inspecting the current schema when no mutations are intended.

        The index states, such as failure messages and population progress, are not captured in the snapshot, but are instead queried "live". This means that if an index in the snapshot is then later deleted, then querying for the state of the index via the snapshot will throw an IndexNotFoundKernelException.

        Specified by:
        schemaSnapshot in interface StorageReader
        Returns:
        a snapshot of the current schema.
